        <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">David Korn</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Response</ENAMEX> to <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Ross McKinney</ENAMEX>'s <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Viewpoint</ENAMEX>
        There are many similarities between the position espoused by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Ross McKinney</ENAMEX> and my
