        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">fosters</ENAMEX> public cynicism and distrust of the motives of academic biomedical <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">researchers</ENAMEX>. The
        protective mechanisms recommended by <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">McKinney</ENAMEX> are opaque to the public and reflect a
        “business as usual” image that fails fully to account for the markedly changed
