        interests.
        By contrast, the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">American Association of Medical Colleges</ENAMEX> formulation urges that any
        institutional involvement in clinical research involving human <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">participants</ENAMEX> in the presence
        of financial conflicts must be predicated on the presence or absence within the institution
